These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
There 7 different types of food: apple, apricot, kiwi, pineapple, radish, raspberry, spinach
There are 7 different nationalities: american, brazilian, french, german, mexican, russian, spanish
 1. the person eating kiwi is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating pineapple is not the russian##6
 3. the american is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
 4. the spanish is somewhere to the right of the mexican##5
 5. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3
 6. the american is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
 7. the person eating raspberry is somewhere between the person eating apricot and the brazilian##7
 8. the brazilian is on the left of the spanish##1
 9. the german is somewhere between the person eating radish and the french##7
10. the french is on the left or right of the american##3
11. the mexican is on the far left##1
12. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the left of the spanish##5
13. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the right of the person eating raspberry##5
14. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the right of the person eating radish##5
15. the person eating radish is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Food          | kiwi    | apple    | apricot | raspberry | pineapple | radish    | spinach |
| Nationality   | mexican | american | french  | russian   | german    | brazilian | spanish |

