 4. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
 5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
 6. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is somewhere between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the snowmobile##7
 8. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far left##1
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is golf##5
10. the person who's sport is tennis is in an even position##4
11. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is lacrosse##7
12. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
13. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
14. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5
